OL,3,CMP urges Chancellor to protect
OL,4,Chospital upgrade as building schemes
OL,5,Cpaused
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat MP Steve Darling has
OL,8,Furged the new Labour Chancellor to
OL,9,Fprotect plans to upgrade Torbay's
OL,10,Fhospital, as hundreds of schemes have
OL,11,Fbeen put on pause.
OL,13,FIn a letter to Rachel Reeves that he
OL,14,Fshared on the social media platform X,
OL,15,Fthe new MP said he was "disappointed"
OL,16,Fto hear there was no money to fund the
OL,17,Fscheme.
