OL,4,Chospital upgrade as building schemes
OL,5,Cpaused
OL,7,FIt comes after the new Chancellor said
OL,8,F"tough choices" would need to be made
OL,9,Fin a bid to deal with the
OL,10,F"catastrophic" state of public
OL,11,Ffinances.
OL,13,FAlong with scrapping a number of local
OL,14,Finfrastructure schemes, Ms Reeves said
OL,15,Fon Monday that the government's new
OL,16,Fhospital building programme will be
OL,17,Freviewed.
