OL,5,Cpaused
OL,7,FMr Darling told ITV News West
OL,8,FCountry's political correspondent Lucy
OL,9,FMcDaid that he had "yet to fully find
OL,10,Fout" what Ms Reeves' announcement will
OL,11,Fmean for Torbay Hospital.
OL,13,FHe said: "I'm just really shocked and
OL,14,Fdisappointed by the state that the
OL,15,Feconomy's been left in by the previous
OL,16,FConservative administration and the
OL,17,Flack of honesty about some of the
OL,18,Fproblems that we're facing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
