OL,4,Chospital upgrade as building schemes
OL,5,Cpaused
OL,7,FThe MP added that he was keen to meet
OL,8,Fwith the Health Secretary, Wes
OL,9,FStreeting, and the Chancellor to
OL,10,F"champion the needs" of Torbay
OL,11,FHospital, where he said 80% of the
OL,12,Festate was recently identified as
OL,13,F"poor or bad quality".
OL,15,FTorbay MP Steve Darling has written to
OL,16,Fthe Chancellor Rachel Reeves, asking
OL,17,Fher to spare Torbay Hospital from the
OL,18,Fswathe of cuts she announced on Monday
OL,19,F29 July.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
