OL,7,FMr Darling went on to say that "in the
OL,8,Flast Care Quality Commission review of
OL,9,FTorbay Hospital, a key part of it was
OL,10,Fthe poor quality of the
OL,11,Finfrastructure...which is just
OL,12,Fabsolutely damning.
OL,14,F"It promoted how the staff were very
OL,15,Fgood but they were having to deal with
OL,16,Finadequate facilities."
OL,18,FIn a message to his constituents, the
OL,19,FMP added: "I think that the case is
OL,20,Funstoppable for the renewal of Torbay.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
