OL,3,CMP urges Chancellor to protect
OL,4,Chospital upgrade as building schemes
OL,5,Cpaused
OL,7,F"The previous Government were only
OL,8,Fgoing to renew 50% of the hospital. I
OL,9,Fwant to make sure that we get a proper
OL,10,Fjob and get that 80% sorted, rather
OL,11,Fthan the half measures we were having
OL,12,Fpreviously proposed.
OL,14,F"I will be pushing the case for Torbay
OL,15,FHospital, I think it's very strong and
OL,16,FI will be meeting with the appropriate
OL,17,Fministers and colleagues at Torbay
OL,18,FHospital to do that."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
